<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<ContentPage xmlns="http://xamarin.com/schemas/2014/forms"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml"
             x:Class="DidacticalEnigma.Xam.Views.DataInitializationPage"
             NavigationPage.HasNavigationBar="False">
    <ContentPage.Content>
        <StackLayout>
            <Label>
The data files must be downloaded. Pressing the button below will make the application do it for you.
The app will ask for permission to access the internet. The size of the download is 150MB.
            </Label>
            <Button Text="Download the data files for me"></Button>
            <Label>
Alternatively you can follow the manual installation process:
Download the files from this site
            </Label>
            <Label Text="Site here"></Label>
            <Label>
And place them in the following directory.
            </Label>
            <Label Text="Data path here"></Label>
            <Label>
Once you've done this, press the following button
            </Label>
            <Button Text="Yes, I have downloaded the data files"></Button>
        </StackLayout>
    </ContentPage.Content>
</ContentPage>